t: Praise*pn the Lord.*s Praise*pn God in his sanctuary; praise*ld him in his mighty heavens.
Praise*ln him for his acts of power; praise*ld him for his surpassing greatness.
Praise*ln him with the sounding of the trumpet, praise*ld him with the harp and lyre,
praise*ln him with timbrel and dancing, praise*ld him with the strings and pipe,
praise*ln him with the clash of cymbals, praise*ld him with resounding cymbals.
Let*pn everything that has breath praise the Lord.*s Praise*pn the Lord.*s
